  "description": "Per-agent up/down state, flapping detection and L3-agent-to-router distribution for a Neutron deployment scraped by openstack-exporter. Answers \"which agents are dead, which are unstable, and is any one network node carrying too many routers?\" — the three failure modes that take tenant networking down.",
